These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, pomegranate, raspberry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, lily, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, jazz, soul
4 different games are played: billiard, chess, go, poker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend, oliveros, bolivar
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person eating broccoli is between the person drinking fanta and the person playing billiard##2
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the person driving the bus and the person playing poker##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the fan of electronic##1
10. the blend-smoker is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is the person who growslily##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Food          | pomegranate | cabbage    | broccoli      | raspberry  |
| Flower         | orchid  | bellflower    | rose       | lily     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | soul       | funk          | electronic |
| Game           | go    | billiard | chess      | poker     |
| Cigar         | bongani   | blend   | oliveros      | bolivar    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

