 1. the dutch is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the spanish is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of gospel##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the nurse##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the fan of soul is the scientist##1
 9. the project-manager is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the fan of indie is on the right of the polish##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the fan of indie is between the designer and the fan of salsa##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
